        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2021-11-04 10:43:24.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 7: Code-Review-1\n\nRegarding \"sdnr\" parts we (highstreet) like to proceed with this change like this:\n- Not mounting this change into gerrit as it is. \nReason: This xlarge amount of changes in one go are to risky that things get broken. The test coverage of Junit and Integration tests in gerrit does not cover enough.\nProposal for proceeding:\n- We synchronize this changes with our local repository where we have more test cases. (We need to do this anyways).\n- In a further step we sync the local repo back to gerrit/master.\n\nWe handle all files that begin with sdnr/...   documenting progress via the Jira-issue\nand not the files with lib/...",
        "patchset_number": 7
      },
      {
        "id": "f60939289d7290739f7f1a47bf5930d14629cbd9",
        "author": {
